{"tid":2201561,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「字節跳動」拒絕微軟收購TikTok計劃 《WSJ》：甲骨文成贏家","createTime":"2020-09-14T01:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T12:50:16.000Z","uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84dcc02ab40989914ed11e4062fa570e28211c25","tid":2201561,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"美國《紐約時報》周日報道，短片分享平台TikTok母公司中國「字節跳動」已經拒絕微軟（Microsoft） 提出的收購TikTok美國業務計劃，令甲骨文（Oracle）成為唯一潛在買家。《華爾街日報》（WSJ）引述消息人士報道，甲骨文已成這次收購的贏家。<br />\n<br />\n微軟發表聲明說，周日已經獲得字節跳動通知，不會向微軟出售TikTok美國業務，但強調其收購計劃對TikTok用戶有利，亦能保障國家安全。<br />\n報道引述涉及賣盤談判人士，字節跳動指出甲骨文將是「可靠技術夥伙」，但不清楚甲骨文會否也收購TikTok多數股權。<br />\n<br />\n美國以國安理由「狙擊」擁有1億美國用戶的TikTok，總統特朗普上月簽署兩道行政命令，迫TikTok賣盤，否則封殺其業務。特朗普早前表明不會延長字節跳動周二前出售或分拆TikTok在美業務的死線。<br />\n美國《紐約時報》／《華爾街日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200914/GXPUIVQDJBD5BDACRHPVPPNZSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200914%2FGXPUIVQDJBD5BDACRHPVPPNZSY%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=5cdd3f26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200914%2FGXPUIVQDJBD5BDACRHPVPPNZSY%2F&h=ff229725\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200914/GXPUIVQDJBD5BDACRHPVPPNZSY/</a>"},{"pid":"0b9b28691a7e64751b9143460a5f218b476f4670","tid":2201561,"uid":156327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"比左個收購方案比侵先喇<br />\n一鳩唔批准你講咩都無用 <br />\n又係借機炒上"},{"pid":"a39bf17683f5774834172009092942908a44e2ae","tid":2201561,"uid":356101,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T01:55:37.000Z","msg":"得番2日時間，呢個時候同人講，得番一個買家，咁呢個買家會唔會大大力壓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3877da930fe7beb7dcfbb03fb64dc08368a6547","tid":2201561,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T01:55:47.000Z","msg":"淨係用